snippet.title: Wreckman - 3DO Interactive Multiplayer Homebrew
snippet.description:
A clone of classic Pacman without Pacman assets, developed by retroloveletter. This is not a port, as existing game source code was not used/adapted for 3DO.

Download the game (and source code) here: https://github.com/retroloveletter/Wreckman
